observe.desc:
[
{There is a tale about a "legendary" creature known as the Blubbering Toad, it is said that popping out its eyes will cause something bizarre to occur.}
]

[
{One day, a warrior heard of the tale and went to the cave of the Blubbering Toad to challenge this mysterious creature. After a fierce battle, the warrior finally succeeded in popping out the eyes of the Blubbering Toad.}
]

[
{Suddenly, the toad's stomach began to bulge as it began to suck in the air around it. Its big eyes flooded with blue tears. Then the toad opened its mouth, enveloping the cave with a gloomy aura. }
]

[
{The warrior realized they had triggered the "bizarre event" the tale mentioned. They were suddenly struck with an overwhelming feeling which caused them to panic, soon after they fell to their knees and silently prayed for whatever was about to come, to not harm them.}
]

[
{The Blubbering Toad began to cry, its tears fell like rain, and the whole cave was filled with sorrow and sadness. The warrior who witnessed this scene felt immense sadness in their heart.}
]

[
{“How can I make it stop crying?”}
]
